                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4585" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0139</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8960 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">是谁击碎了梦想——藏格控股股东利益侵占</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Who broke the dream？ Occupation of Zangge Holding shareholders</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">朱清香，李志宇，郜小玉，张可欣，许楠，李小青</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">河北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘宏</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李志宇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">藏格控股</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">藏格控股；股东利益侵占；股权质押；关联交易</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Occupation of shareholders&#39; interests; Zangge Holding; equity pledge; related transaction</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019年，瑞华事务所针对公司年报出具了的保留意见，与此同时来自深交所23项疑问的问询函也抵达藏格控股，藏格控股的股东资产侵占再也无法隐瞒，从2016年公司借款上市，到如今的处罚累累，藏格控股三年的起伏最终变为了“*ST藏格”，而这样的结果其实由来已久。本案例的开始可以追溯到2016年，藏格控股准备借壳上市前，公司财务部职员李某入职，从此开始见证了公司从2016年到2018年的发展，以及控股股东肖永明在这三年利用其绝对控股地位进行利益侵占的过程。本案例旨在让学员了解控股股东利益侵占的动机、做法，分析利益侵占对利益相关者的损害，尤其是中小股东的利益损害，及由此导致的公司市值以及未来发展的影响。深度思考健全的董事会治理结构及培育公开透明的资本市场对中小股东相关保护的意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In 2019, Ruihua CPA firm issued a reservation on the company ’s annual report. At the same time, 23 enquiries from the Shenzhen Stock Exchange also reached Zangge Holdings. Zangge ’s shareholder asset embezzlement can no longer be concealed. From 2016 The company borrowed money to go public, and now the punishment is heavy, and the three-year ups and downs of Zangge Holdings eventually became &quot;* ST Zangge&quot;, and such a result has a long history. The beginning of this case can be traced back to 2016. Before Zange Holdings prepared to backdoor listing, the company&#39;s finance department employee Mr.Li joined the company. Since then, he has witnessed the company&#39;s development from 2016 to 2018, and the controlling shareholder Xiao Yongming used in the past three years. Its absolute controlling position carries on the process of interest encroachment. This case aims to enable trainees to master different methods of shareholder interest encroachment, understand the damage to the interests of stakeholders, especially small and medium shareholders, and even affect the company&#39;s market value and future development. , Deepen the protection of small and medium shareholders related to corporate governance.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内部治理或股权结构对中小股东的利益保护以及相关治理措施</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020-08</td>
                            </tr>
